tags.name: Nueva Loja
Former San Rafael Cascada
tags.note: On 2 February 2020, the San Rafael Cascada disappeared. The Rio Coca eroded behind the hard rock that formed the waterfall, eventually flowing under the former waterfall. The Rio Coca now flows under the former waterfall and through a natural arch.
